import { Stack } from "@mui/material"
import { colors } from "../../utils/CustomTheme"
import { puzzleInputs } from "../../utils/PuzzleInputs"
import { PuzzleInput } from "../Atoms"
import { usePuzzleState } from "../Atoms/PuzzleInput"

const HomePage = () => {
    const puzzleState = usePuzzleState(puzzleInputs[14].real)
    return <Stack justifyContent="center" alignItems="center">
        <PuzzleInput puzzleState={puzzleState} sx={{ width: "80vw", border: `1px solid ${colors.saffron}` }} />
    </Stack>

}

export default HomePage
